1. patchTool
============

fast handle patch merge/format/am an so on


2. format
=========

2.1 format patch by commitlist
------------------------------

python ~/github/python-me/prj/pathTool/patchTool.py  --commitlist commitlist -d patche

2.1 format patch to attend author and upstream
----------------------------------------------

	(1) only patch

	    patchTool.py --fm *.patch

	(2) only patch with extra

	    patchTool.py --fm *.patch -fmex openeuler

	(3) only patch with extra + mail

	    --fm xx.patch  --fmex openeuler --fmma "Zou Cao <zoucao@kernelsoft.com>"

	(4) only patch with extra + mail in dirctory

	    --fm xx.patch  --fmex openeuler --fmma "Zou Cao <zoucao@kernelsoft.com>"

